name: DinoFacts

”Alexa, open dino facts and tell me about dinos.”
”what is a dinosaur.”
”tell me about a long time ago.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dino facts
des: Many kids grow up with a fascination for dinosaurs (in other words, dinos) referring to the many great and massive creatures that roamed our planet 65 million years ago. Feed your child's imagination and knowledge with this amazing skill, where Alexa will provide a fact or idea about dinosaurs that you probably may not have known before. Dive in, and have fun with this interesting and educational skill from Alexa!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
